   SUBJECT: Transmittal Memorandum for Operations Manual Issuance 74-22

   TO: All Holders of Operations Manual

   1. Material Transmitted:

   Revised Chapter A-19, Reporting of Weather Modification Activities.

   2. Summary:

   The revised chapter states the due date for report. It also calls
   attention to the need to obtain information on the environmental and
   safety aspects of a weather modification project.

   3. Effect on Other Instructions:

   Replaces Chapter A-19, "Reporting of Weather Modification Activities,"
   dated August 12, 1974, issuance number 74-18.

   George P. Cressman
   Director, National Weather Service
